Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a huge wall that stands in front of you becomes\Na large door if you change the way you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master and apprentice, a complicated play\Nworld, key is the fish that glitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,looks like a kid but has the grown up intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his name is Meitantei Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what was it where the people leave to and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hmmnn what was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmmmn what was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the people live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,5th number of Bekachou, 39th street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point in telling your own address?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what is the next dialogue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you already forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already been a week, just memorise it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: name of places
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Burakouji of Yaburakouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: sound of crying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,paipo, paipo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,oh, yes, "paipo, paipo and pom okorin\Nyah pompokorin and doukendin yah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:40.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: pompokorin means raccoon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuuringan of paipo paipo, fuuringan of shuuringan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:50.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: those are all name of places\Nand Chousuke is a name of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,fuuringan of pompokopee of pompokopee of pompokona\Nof choshuuman of Chousuke, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, why don't you quit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you are able to memorise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I know your intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's all about all-you-can-drink, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be doing this,\Nyou could be a laughing-stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't have such...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you going to the stage already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are very motivated, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:22.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Uajima Nagarou (50)\NOwner of criminal protecting goods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a good image as.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is going to do a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Uajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who looks after me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still telling me to quit this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But lets make the dialogue an easier\None so you can memorise it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a new fence in my neighbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This level suits you best...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:56.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE SANMA CASE OF MEGURO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is Master Ichimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu, lets do our best today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ichimatsu (55)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've known each other for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to be my apprentice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I told him to come after graduating from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uajima, let's have some tea, all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the master of play doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's helping out at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spring came to the master,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now he is out from his bachelor life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:52.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Meguro Mira (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of fish is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Sanma
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a lot. Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you have Sanina of Meguro today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master's Sanma of Meguro is incredible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,one who hears the rumors must come to the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that is the Sanma you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is Sanma of Meguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanma of Meguro is a Rakugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time ago there was a stupid king, and\None day he went to hunt birds to Meguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he got treat in a small house\Nthere he ate his first fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was surprised by the taste of Sanma and when he went\Nto another place, he said, "I want to eat Sanma again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Sanma for the king was free of oil and bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In concerns for the king's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king asked where the Sanma was from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,surprised at the obvious difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his servant replied, This is a\Nfresh Sanma I brought from Toushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the king said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meguro is the place for Sanma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch! I cut my finger with a broken plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are going to the stage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, your play is at 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it, it's 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay then, we are going on the stage before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman is the wife of apprentice\Nof master Ichimatsu, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, his name is Kusaburou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she's his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:07:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's divorced with him and now\Nthe master is looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My instinct tells me that the master\Nis also helping her out financially.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am afraid that the master is being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Generally, who will be sociable with an old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that master Ichimatsu is loaded,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am afraid that she is after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... people can't be judged by their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this only the tale that a fairy exists in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,its paipo o paipo shuuringan a shuurig hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,its fence a fence from before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that the neighbour has made a new fence, Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,fence, fence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is a new fence on the land, cooooooooool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am afraid of my ability to make everyone laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did not make the people laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you yourself were laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I want to follow your style too sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This fish, where is this fish from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:09:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the fresh fish brought from city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, Meguro is the place for fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, you have to be my company tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will be the champion next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you're gonna do this again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, go ahead, because some\Nguests may be coming to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to clean up the stage,\Nplease wait for me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohh, Uajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like his work is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, I am going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Master Ichimatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His guest has not come yet, so he told us to go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Master Ichimatsu was stabbed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A telephone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, someone called and said Master Ichimatsu was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plenty amount of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was discovered unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot tell yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written, "Meguro's"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be the Sanma of Meguro that he did earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to write Meguro's Sanma and\Nsuccumbed that might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,these letters, it's almost illegible,\Nbut it is written "Meguro".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hmm... Meguro... sanma of Meguro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer! I've know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, it is me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was me who stabbed the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this knife belong you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why on earth did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me explain on behalf of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you are in a debt to the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you thought if you killed the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you didn't have to return the debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk on the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did not do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manragutei Kisaburou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,apprentice of the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me who stabbed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stole the knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from this woman's shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stabbed the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he not your Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer! He's lying to protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like being popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I was also in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think he should have kicked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that is the motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaburou really loves Rakugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sure he wants to come back to the stage again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such man would not do anything of this sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These letters that master wrote is the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanma of Meguro,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's the tale I used to practice most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:13:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he didn't do anything, I did everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two are protecting each other\Nthinking that other is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does this message mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it Ichimatsu was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, a guest is supposed\Nto come, so please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was he waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meeting at 7 o'clock... Meruhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no mistake about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, we will find out the detailed facts in the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohhh... hit came again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two have nothing to do with this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitaburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to meet Master Ichimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time was when we were returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be a bit before 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw that he was already stabbed\Nand there was a knife beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you thought it was Miya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Miya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw Kisaburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nentering this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:15:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got out of the room\Nas soon as he saw Ichimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Miya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} thought that it was\NKisaburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who stabbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you saw me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because... I am the greatest fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you got arrested. I thought that and.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you, how could you have thought\Nthat I stabbed Master Ichimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I am supposed to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd never hurt the Master Ichimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, then stop both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu wrote the name\Nof the culprit on this board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This "Of Meguro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it does not look like a name of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Master Ichimatsu's\Nbag is under the white board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look through the notebook inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and read his schedule of tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meetin at 7 o'clock. Naruheso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Naruheso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that "Naruheso" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is written Naruheso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, Master Ichimatsu had a wound on his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably wrote that with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to write Meruhen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meruhen becomes Naruheso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, please turn and see for yourself\Nthe letters on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter "Me" becomes "Na",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when its tilted, the letter "Gu" looks like "Ga",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ro" remains same but "No" become a sign to lengthen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what does that read?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... "NaGaRooooo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stay with us a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu wrote your name Nagaroo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which meant that he wanted to tell\Nus that the culprit was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, what nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you yourself know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I do not have time to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please look at hole above.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a bag
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made Conan search for it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From there, you can see that this\Nroom is connected to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please check inside the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the doll for protecting criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you put beside the woman to\Nshow that she is with a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which can be bought from the shop of Uajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put it beside the window and made us think,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you where working at your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and entered this room from above, and you stabbed\Nthe Master with the knife you prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you returned as if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, that is not true! It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the evidence? Where is the\Nevidence that I am the culprit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, there is a speaker attached to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search near the speaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there must be a M.D recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M.D recorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this, the switch is on, so that\Nyou can know the condition of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu told me that earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Ichimatsu Master was not listening to my play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the switch was not on. But now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever turned on the switch probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wanted to record the play of the Master secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please forward the tape and play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, Meguro is the place for fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, recorder's nowadays is capable of\Nrecording for a long time unlike the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the moment of the incident\Nmust be recorded in the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please backward it to that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagaro! What are you doing! Nagaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miya does not listen to me anymore because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything stupid! Miya is\Nwaiting Kisaburou to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmhmhmhmmhm... damned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop! It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stole the knife from Miya's shop and stabbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will give it to you. It's the tape of Master Ichimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanma of Meguro is also here. So give up your M.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can understand that you like\Nthe play of Master Ichimatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but never record it illegally again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Kisaburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got a call from hospital and they\Nsay that Master Ichimatsu will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is cruel of you to think that I am the culprit\Njust by seeing me getting out from his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you had a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, the kind of the knife she saw might be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I should give it to the Master so he could\Neat this fresh fish that I got this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you thought it was a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you had a scary and gloomy look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you are clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would think that a fish is a knife, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanma is written as "The Fish of Sword of Autumn". So,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Ichimatsu's life is not in danger. So how about,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you two eat this fish together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, we have to visit the Master Ichimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will plead for you and tell him that\Nyou want to be his apprentice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will definitely forgive you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was waiting for you to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should not be a dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, conan, you are crying coz you are moved by my play?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is say that child sleeps getting bored always,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it is the power of my play\Nthat it does not happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not sleeping because you are\Noccupying my place for sleeping.
